data.description: If you've dreamed of owning your own home with in a nice, peaceful area, this is your opportunity! The home is a 2-bedroom 1 bath just over 0.25 acre.  Come check out this charming single-family home! Please note it was built 2010.   Property is currently rented for $1000/mo. The tenant is on a month-to-month lease.  Best of all, there are no HOA fees! Property is located between Bronson and Williston, just 10 min from Cedar Lake Woods and Gardens Park or you can go for snorkeling In the Prehistoric Devil's Den.  Don’t let opportunity pass you by!
